# Indexer cache — written by the LSP/IDE server into each project's
# .vscode/. Never check it in (committed copies invalidate when
# INDEX_VERSION bumps and confuse fixture-based tests). The `.json`
# entry is left for users upgrading from pre-v29 caches.
.vscode/callchain-index.msgpack
.vscode/callchain-index.json
test/fixtures/**/.vscode/
